                            </figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <div class="leadership-box-copy col-lg-12">
                            <p tabindex="0" role="article">Elected by the Republican Conference, the Majority Leader helps plan the legislative agenda for the House and schedules legislative business.</p>
                            <p class="links-group">
                                <a href="/members/M001165" title="View Profile" class="library-link">View Profile</a>
                                <a href="https://www.majorityleader.gov/" target="_blank" title="Visit Website" class="library-link">Visit Website</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
